  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink37-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaḷaic cūḷiṉāl teḷittāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa kātaṟparattai talaimakaṭkup
          pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpat taṉ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink37">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻna</l>
          <l>ṉayantō ruṇkaṇ pacantupaṉi malka</l>
          <l>vallaṉ vallaṉ poytta</l>
          <l>ṟēṟṟā ṉuṟṟa cūḷvāyt tallē</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Alas, [my] friend!</l>
          <l>The bringer of joy</l>
          <l>that big, strong man</l>
          <l>[even ]as the kajal-eyes of the women who yearn for him grow dim and fill with dew-like tears, </l>  
          <l>does not admit that the [words of] the vow that had taken place, [even as they were] becoming true,</l> 
           <l>were lies.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
